 `docker_service.py` — Required for build/publish operations\n- `k8s_provider.py` — Required for Kubernetes deployments\n- `agentcube_provider.py` — Required for AgentCube platform integration\n- `BuildRuntime`, `PublishRuntime`, `InvokeRuntime`, `StatusRuntime` — Stub only (return `{\"status\": \"not_implemented\"}`)\n- `build`, `publish`, `invoke`, `status` CLI commands — Registered but not functional\n\n**Examples:**\n- `examples/hello-agent/main.py` — Documentation/example gap\n- `examples/math-agent/main.py` — Documentation/example gap\n\n---\n\n### 📊 Compliance Summary\n\n| Metric | Value |\n|--------|-------|\n| **Pack Command Specific** | **100% ✅** |\n| **Overall Compliance** | **73%** (14/19 requirements) |\n| **Status** | **APPROVED** — Pack command ready for use |\n\nThe pack command is **complete and functional**. Missing items are either **test coverage** (deferred) or **dependencies for other CLI commands** (out of AR-020 scope).","time":{"start":1775886411740,"end":1775886411740}}}
